attributes.Long form description: The student exchanges the battery at the beginning, continues by changing the SD card, and accidentally flips the battery to the wrong side in the process. The student tries to turn on the GoPro after that, but the instructor has to ask to flip the battery to the right position before the student manages to turn it on. After that, the student turns off the GoPro, and ensembles it into the strap.  Then assembles it to the handgrip and finally to the tripod. At the very end, the student disassembles the GoPro from the tripod and finishes up the video.
